- Download the openshift setup file for linux from follow source:
    - https://github.com/minishift/minishift/releases

- After downloaded, extract the setup folder from zip/tar archive
- would be have installed the virtualbox tool

- cd path_to_extracted_setup_folder
- ls -l (and should be the minishift script file)
- ./minishift start --vm-driver virtualbox (and wait few minutes)

- ussualy returned after download/setup follow:
  "https:your_ip:8443/console"
  "credentials: oc login -u system:admin"

- Acces from your default browser:
- https:your_ip:8443/console with credentials: oc login -u system:admin